GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PositioningThesis> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PositioningThesis> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#PositioningThesis> ;
    narr:childCount "122"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "15e06f57ba5835c4cf2ec859ee578151b0f59cae" ;
    narr:narration """The positioning of aswritten has evolved from a developer-focused enterprise tool into a thesis on [expertise installation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation) as a fundamental layer of knowledge distribution. This trajectory is anchored by the [three-era framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TrustedInformationEra) of books, search, and now curated expertise. Market focus shifted from enterprise to [SMB and B2C](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_B2CPivot) as the primary volume play, eventually resolving into a [tier-continuum](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TierContinuumNotDistinctMarkets) where Expert, Team, and Org use cases are unified by the same [memory substrate](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AswrittenIsMemorySubstrate). Recent refinements emphasize [anti-monoculture](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiMonocultureAmplifier) and the [CEO-as-context-server](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CEOContextServerReframe) pain point, while the GTM has inverted from selling a tool to [consulting-as-product-delivery](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingIsMeUsingProduct). The thesis now distinguishes between [perspective and information](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveVsInformation), positioning aswritten as the [steering memory](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SteeringDecisionProcess) for AI agents, effectively fighting [Chinese Whispers](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ChineseWhispersProvenance) through full provenance.""" ;
